### Package manager

- Always use `pnpm`.

### Install

```bash
pnpm install
```

### Development

```bash
pnpm dev          # Chromium default
pnpm dev:chrome   # Chrome
pnpm dev:firefox  # Firefox
pnpm dev:edge     # Edge
```

### Build & bundle

```bash
pnpm build        # current target
pnpm build:all    # all browsers
pnpm zip          # produce distributable zip
```

### Quality

```bash
pnpm lint         # ESLint
pnpm typecheck    # tsc
pnpm format       # Prettier
```

### Tests

```bash
pnpm test         # run once
pnpm test:watch   # watch mode
pnpm test:ui      # UI runner
pnpm test -- --coverage  # coverage
```
